defaultRestaurants.name: Dunkin’ Donuts
defaultRestaurants.description: Dunkin’ Donuts in Paradise Palms Cafe will keep Hawaii running with high-quality beverage offerings–including freshly-brewed Hot and Iced Coffees–paired perfectly with delicious donuts, bakery goods, sandwiches and more.

defaultRestaurants.name: Lasoon
defaultRestaurants.description:
Lasoon offers natural home-cooked Nepali and Indian food for everyone. From a $5 bowl options when you are in a hurry to larger plates to please your appetite.
We are focusing on vegan and gluten free meals and offer 4 – 5 options that are changed daily. Besides the vegan options we offer 3 meat options ranging from mild to spicy!

defaultRestaurants.name: Holoholo Grill
defaultRestaurants.description: Holoholo Grill features healthy, locally grown salads, sandwiches, and grab-and-go items at affordable prices. They are committed to using the freshest island-grown ingredients sourced directly from farmers and fishermen. Grab-and-go, breakfast items, or catering for any sized group are also available!

defaultRestaurants.name: L&L Hawaiian Barbecue
defaultRestaurants.description: Delicious local and Asian-American fusion cuisine served in big portions at reasonable prices! Try delicious L&L favorites like the Hawaiian Barbecue beef, chicken, or short ribs! Enjoy L&L’s famous fried chicken katsu, the best in town! Grab-and-go, breakfast items and party packs for groups also available.

defaultRestaurants.name: Le Crêpe Café
defaultRestaurants.description:
Le Crêpe Café makes traditional French crêpes, cooked to order in front of customers. They specialize in a flavorsome menu of sweet and savory crêpes and use fresh ingredients, organic when possible. Their utensils are even bio-compostable. Enjoy a crêpe any time of day, as a breakfast, snack, main course, or dessert — close your eyes and you’re in Paris!
Whether you’re needing a break from the law books or a pick-me-up as you’re headed to or off campus, you’ll also appreciate Le Crêpe Café’s French Roast and espresso drinks.

defaultRestaurants.name: Panda Express
defaultRestaurants.description:
Panda Express serves gourmet Chinese food made with only the freshest ingredients. Famous for its Orange Chicken, they also offer a number of Wok Smart entrées that contain less than 250 calories per serving, such as Shanghai Angus Steak, Kung Pao Chicken, and Broccoli Beef. Other favorites include Beijing Beef, Sweetfire Chicken Breast, and Honey Walnut Shrimp.
Panda Express’ offerings can be enjoyed in Panda Bowls, or two and three item plates. Perfect for lunch, dinner or as a pick-me-up snack between classes.

defaultRestaurants.name: The Burger Shop
defaultRestaurants.description: The Campus Center Food Court offers a variety of food including plate lunches, bentos, grab-and-go salads and wraps, burgers, and more!

defaultRestaurants.name: Bowlful
defaultRestaurants.description: The Campus Center Food Court offers a variety of food including plate lunches, bentos, grab-and-go salads and wraps, burgers, and more!

defaultRestaurants.name: Subway
defaultRestaurants.description: Feeling hungry? Stop by Subway for some delicious sandwiches and salads made fresh. Subway also offers dessert and breakfast items such as pastries and cookies.

defaultRestaurants.name: Starbucks
defaultRestaurants.description:
With a full menu, as well as seasonal and specialty items, coffee fanatics are sure to be pleased. Also available are pastries, fruit cups, and bottled beverages for your purchase.
 Our location strives to give you the very same experience found at any other Starbucks across the nation.

defaultRestaurants.name: Jamba Juice
defaultRestaurants.description:
Visit Jamba for refreshing fruit smoothie blends, delicious and nutritious energy bowls, fresh juices, healthy baked goods and savory grab-and-go food items.
 Jamba blends real fruit and whole ingredients into each delicious fresh juice, smoothie, or energy bowl you order and contains no artificial colors, preservatives, or flavors.

defaultRestaurants.name: Ba-Le
defaultRestaurants.description:
Located at Hemenway Hall, Ba-Le is the perfect stop if you're craving something a little different.
 Pastries, sandwiches, and pre-made salads are some of their quick lunch options. Popular items at Ba-Le include pho, pad thai, and banh mi sandwiches.
 Also offered at Ba-Le are a selection of La Tour Cafe macarons and entrees.
 Spend your meal time at Ba-Le for a variety of foods and flavors!

defaultRestaurants.name: Serg’s Mexican Kitchen
defaultRestaurants.description: Brings to Hawaii the essential spices and unique flavors of traditional Mexican cooking. With original roots from Mexico City, and educated in the culinary arts, Serg has worked at fine dining restaurants and major hotels in Las Vegas, Nevada. He is bringing back to life a slow style of cooking taught to him by his parents. Many of these dishes are made from scratch and using only fresh ingredients in a relaxed atmosphere.

defaultRestaurants.name: Waipuna Sushi
defaultRestaurants.description: Waipuna Sushi specializes in ahi poke, salmon poke, tako poke, and custom platters. For more information and photos, please visit: www.waipunasushi.com

defaultRestaurants.name: Asia Manoa
defaultRestaurants.location: 2801 E Manoa Rd # C Honolulu, HI 96822
defaultRestaurants.description: Simple storefront restaurant serves familiar Chinese dishes plus combo platters & daily specials.

defaultRestaurants.name: Nishi Moncho Ramen
defaultRestaurants.description: Are you in the mood for delicious food using fresh ingredients at an affordable price? If so, then we are the destination for you. Nishi Moncho Ramen Restaurant offers authentic Ramen and delicious tasting Japanese cuisine in Honolulu, HI. Our convenient location and affordable prices make our restaurant a natural choice for eat-in or take-out meals in the Honolulu community. Our restaurant is known for its variety in taste and high quality fresh ingredients. Come and experience our friendly atmosphere and excellent service.

defaultRestaurants.name: Andy’s Sandwiches & Smoothies
defaultRestaurants.description:
LOOKING FOR A HEALTHY AND GREAT TASTING MEAL? 
 Come on in and select from our variety of freshly made sandwiches, salads, soups, smoothies, and baked goods. 
 The Special of the Day is always a good pick! We offer take-out and delivery via BiteSquad and DoorDash. Checks and most major credit cards accepted.
